      <p>The portable power station market has exploded in the last two years, and contractors are the biggest beneficiaries. With LiFePO₄ battery technology maturing, solar charging becoming standard, and capacities reaching 3600Wh in a wheelable package, there's never been a better time to replace your gas generator.</p>
